<div class="img-wrap">
<div class="thumb">
<img alt="Children pose on motorcycles belonging to the members of the group Bikers for Humanity during an eyesight examination event, in Nucsoara, Romania, Saturday, May 29, 2021. (AP Photo/Vadim Ghirda)" src="https://gdb.voanews.com/613B4810-1698-4CA4-B9A7-BF0CB623CFF3_w250_r0_s.jpg" />
</div>
